    "body": "*Sigh* I didn't notice that one, or didn't think about it enough. I'm annoyed that we removed something that large numbers of extensions still recommend people use. I think we've been very over-aggressive with the deprecation here. But as it's done, and we don't have waves of protest, so I guess we should probably go ahead and remove this code."
